Best mates Jeff McCubbery and Ian Bullock devised Captain Cootie Cards to counter the influx of lingo from overseas . 
  The pair have devised a range of greeting cards, coffee mugs and calendars emblazoned with Aussie slang . 
  They met on a fishing trip 20 years ago and vowed to keep Aussie lingo alive . 
  But the pair were spurned by the companies they pitched to . 
 